Package: torpor
Type: Package
Title: Assigning metabolic rate measurements to torpor and euthermia in heterothermic endotherms  
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Colin",
             family = "Vullioud",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
